message.body: Careful of those tornados
are y'all under tornado watch?
No. I heard there is some in GA and it might head up here
ah. yeah. the weather is sucky.
How are you today?
really good. how are you?
Just normal good. What makes you really good?
i'm just having a really good day. slept really well, only one class (which i was prepared for), got to go to target to get valentine's stuff, etc. anything especially normal good?
Not really. I have to order a computer case for my friends computer I'm putting together because the case I was gonna use had old wiring.
What did you want to buy for valentines day? Lol
Aaand I sent you an email
i think it's cool that you can do computery stuff like that. i was getting stuff to make valentines with and new window decorations. i have gel clings for like every holiday.
That's cute. What's your book about?
Ill get you some gel glings for my birthday. Great holiday.
which book?
Uh light reading slut book?
ah. yeah. shan actually picked it up. i'm not sure how i feel about it so far.
you said you're a LotR fan right?
uhhh. if reading a third of the hobbit counts as being a fan, then yes.
Haha. Oh nevermind you. I wanna find more common ground so I can make inside jokes or references.
In your response email send me a list of your top 10 or 15 favorite movies in order
yes sir. :)
okay I'm home so I'm taking a shower and then hitting the sheets, sweetheart. Good night
night. thank you for everything.
i just accidentally sent you like 3 emails. enjoy.
how are you doing today babe?
eh. pretty good now.
how are you?
I'm doing great. I've gotten some stuff done and got a nice email.
...or 3, haha. normal great or exceptionally great?
Or "like" 3. Not quite. But like it. I'm doing as great as can be expected short of getting sexy pics from you ;)
well, i'm feeling decidedly unsexy today, so i don't really imagine that happening.
Haha. I didn't ask though. I'm just letting you know what makes me feel really great. You are sexy today.
What makes you happy?
And what makes you feel sexy and unsexy?

i feel sexy when i'm wearing flattering/sexy clothes. and when i catch guys looking at me in that way or like chatting me up or whatever. i feel unsexy on days like today, when i'm wearing this enormous men's shirt thing and i've got my hair pulled back.
also when my eyes are really swollen. not sexy.
Why are your eyes swollen, baby?
they really aren't, today. just a little from rubbing them because i'm so tired. but any time i cry my eyes are always like crazy swollen the next day.
I wish I could have kissed your tears away, and I want to make you feel sexy. I bet you look cute with your hair pulled back. :)
you're sweet.
Sorry I will try to dial it back a bit. Be more of an ass. I couldn't tell from the pic if you look good with hair up. Your smile was in the way.
i was trying to distract with the smile.
when I first started getting pictures from you, you refused to smile
i still don't love it, but i didn't want to send you, like, a frowny snap.
I love when your lips are parted a little in an asymmetrical smile
Good morning glory!
morning. :) i'm just headed into yoga, text you later?
How long is the yoga class? I'm bored waiting for your text :(
it was just until 12 but then i got a call from someone i was going to hang out with today so i had to hurry and get ready. i didn't realize you were waiting by the phone. :P
Oh I was waiting by the phone. Holding my breath even.
Oh where oh where is my Krunke? Oh where oh where could she be?
I was gonna make a comment about the game but then realized you probably don't care lol
i did, however, learn who was playing a couple hours ago.
Bunch of gay guys beating a bunch of black guys
didn't it just start?
Yea and I just got off work. They predict 49ers win by 3 but I'm a baltimore fan sorta. Lived in md a couple years
uhhuh. are you going to a superbowl party?
Yea. And ravens are my adopted team
did you win? (is it over?)
Yea lol
